# Frappe Bench (myerp/) -- ERPNext and Frappe Framework are pinned, unforked
# upstream dependencies (Story 1.1 / Architecture AD-1), never modified or
# pushed to. Whitelist pattern: ignore everything under myerp/ except
# apps/our_brand (our own code, from Story 1.2 on) -- explicit exclusion
# lists proved unsafe here (missed a site_config.json containing a real
# auto-generated DB password, per-site logs, and a stray screenshot).
myerp/*
!myerp/apps
myerp/apps/*
!myerp/apps/our_brand
